HT1AUD.original: ~z~If you ever feel like exploring the skies again, remember Higgins!
~z~It was recently targeted by terrorists in Weazel's 72.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~最近在Weazel电视台的《72小时》中成为了恐怖分子的目标。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~I've seen land laid to waste by war, and I'm here to tell you,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~我曾见过战争造成的焦土。我告诉你，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~First up, the Daily Globe Building, home to all the LC news,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~首先是环球日报大厦，自由城一切新闻的大本营。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~The harbor, where complaining immigrants arrive by the masses.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~港口，满腹牢骚的移民自此涌入。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Every day, Algonquin residents are grateful that this is here to keep us separate from Alderney.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~每天，Algonquin的居民都很感激这条河让我们与Alderney划清界限。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~this won't be in guide books, you'd have to be one extreme tourist. Gnarly.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~旅游指南都忽略这里，只有硬核旅行者会来。很好。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Look out to sea folks, the view goes for miles.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~看看这片海吧，风景绵延数英里。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~I'm Jase, you're in safe hands, I could fly this baby with my eyes shut.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~我是Jase，值得你们信赖，这飞机闭着眼睛我都会开。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Sharks would explain some of the things swept up on the beach,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~有鲨鱼倒是能解释被冲上海滩的一些东西了，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Well, if you're going to do it, do it right, huh?
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~对了，你有想法的话，自己上桥，懂？

HT1AUD.original: ~z~she's dirty, she's deep and she has her secrets, you betcha...
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~她肮脏，她深沉，她有她的秘密，没错...

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Hi, welcome to Higgins Tour, I'm Vicki, I'm your pilot.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~嗨，欢迎参加Higgins观光，我叫Vicki，是你的飞行员。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~if you look down now folks, you'll see three generations refusing to help themselves.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~现在往下看的话，你会看见自甘沉沦的三代人。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~bodies, torn up as if by artillery. That, or giant teeth.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~尸体，如果不是被大炮轰过，就是被尖牙撕裂的。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~I've never been in there, but it sure is popular with you visitors. Full of old stuff, crammed with it.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~我是没进去过，不过你们游客肯定很喜欢。全是古董啥的，都塞满了。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Hi, welcome to your Higgins Tour, I'm Rob,
~z~See the lake? Few people know this,
~z~Okay, well I've had a blast, you folks have been great.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~好了，这次我很高兴，感谢你们的配合。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~where Yusuf Amir is building more apartments for his foreign buddies to live in tax-free.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~建成后Yusuf Amir就能为他的外国哥们提供免税住所了。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~the murders, the robberies and the immigrants taking our jobs.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~从谋杀，到抢劫，还有夺走我们工作的移民。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Folks, welcome to your tour of the LC skies!
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~各位，欢迎参加自由城天际之旅！

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Well, that's us; I hope you've enjoyed LC from the skies!
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~好了，就到这里。希望你喜欢自由城天际的风光！

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Civic Citadel, I once flew the Mayor in this chopper,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~市政厅，我曾开这架直升机带过市长，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Higgins Helitours. We're here to show you Liberty City from the sky.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~Higgins直升机观光，让您从空中一览自由城风光。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~oh yeah, good guy. I mean, I don't vote or anything but nice guy.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~他人挺好。我不是给他拉票，但他人确实好。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Rotterdam Tower, a buddy of mine tried a base jump off that bad boy.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~鹿特丹塔，我的一个朋友试过从它上面跳伞。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Ah, the Majestic Hotel, found in story and in song,
~z~Now the Libertonian, it's closed for renovation,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~接下来是自由城博物馆，因装修暂时闭馆。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~It sure is great to be driving a chopper for fun rather than to mow down a village full of hostiles.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~兴趣使然开直升机可比被迫扫射敌方村庄要好多了。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~but a third of the park's budget goes toward cleaning this fountain of pigeon shit.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~公园管理费有三分之一是用来清理水里的鸽子屎的。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~First, the famous Broker Bridge, used in many movies and TV shows.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~首先，是著名的Broker大桥，许多影视作品的取景地。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~A sight usually reserved for transplant organs and the super rich.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~俯瞰不再是移植器官和超级富豪的特权。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~all manner of ways for chubby, spoiled brats, to get whipped into a sugar frenzy.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~这里无所不用其极，诱使被宠坏的小胖子们陷入糖分狂热。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~you can spot the library, where they get their long hair stuck in their fancy books.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~你可以看见图书馆，学生把自己的长发夹在书里当书签。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Over Westminster now, some of you out-of-towners may never have seen a gay before,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~现在在Westminster，你们这些外地人可能从来没有见过同性恋。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~I've seen war zones folks, and I can tell you, you're looking at one.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~我曾亲眼见过战区，要我说，莫过于此。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~if those sheets could tell stories, right folks?
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~只可惜那些床单不会说话，对吧？

HT1AUD.original: ~z~that makes America the best country in the world.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~这一自由使美国成为世上最好的国家。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Come back for food poisoning or a massage with the happiest ending in the City.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~这里不仅有食物中毒，还有全城最令人愉悦的按摩。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~From us at Higgins, have a nice day and remember that tips are appreciated.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~我谨代表敝公司，祝您生活愉快。别忘记给小费哦。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Workers in the exchange often live here in Castle Gardens.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~证交区的职员大多住在Castle Gardens。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Ah, the housing projects of the world's finest city.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~啊，世界第一城市的公屋社区。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~I will be your guide for today. Buckle up, and no questions about my name.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~是你今天的导游。系好安全带，别在意我的名字。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~That is some serious all-American dough right there, I shit you not. Mon-ey.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~全美国的财富汇聚于此，没骗你。钱哪。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~I always think of this place as like, Algonquin's appendix; it's there, but nobody knows why.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~我一直把这里视作，Algonquin的鸡肋：食之无味，弃之可惜。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Heard the name Kenny Petrovic folks? He's a Hove Beach landmark too,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~听说过Kenny Petrovic吗？他也是Hove Beach的一大标志，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~a den of vice and corruption the likes of which most of you folks will never see again.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~罪恶与腐败的老巢，不过你们很难有机会再次来到这里。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~That statue is such a great emblem of the Freedom of Speech and Expression
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~这尊雕像是表达自由的伟大象征，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~They can concentrate on making money in peace and quiet.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~这里的祥和宁静让他们能够专心赚钱。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~all of East Europe moves in to spread crime like jelly over LC.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~东欧移民蜂拥而入，将犯罪洒遍自由城的土地。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Hove Beach, or Little Sodom as some call it, a nest of sin,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~Hove Beach，又被称为迷你罪都，犯罪的温床，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Cleethorpes Tower, where millionaires can go to the top floor,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~Cleethorpes大楼，只有百万富翁才能前往顶层，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~I need to make clear that Higgins is in no way responsible for any injuries -
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~事先声明，敝公司不对旅途中的任何伤害负责－

HT1AUD.original: ~z~This is the Exchange. High flying workers here are calling in debt
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~这里是证交区，壮志凌云的职员们在这里催债，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~these youngsters taunt death because they've never seen war. Bring back the draft.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~这些年轻人嘲笑死亡，因为他们从未见过战争。就该恢复兵役。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~they say it has fifteen bodies within it's cement.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~据说路面底下埋了十五具尸体。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Even after they tore out its heart.
~z~Don't worry about the name, there is no joke I haven't heard.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~别被我的名字吓到，那个笑话我早听过了。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Warmer waters have led some to speculate there may even be sharks...
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~海水升温甚至让一些人怀疑这里有鲨鱼...

HT1AUD.original: ~z~lean over the marble balcony, and spit on ordinary Americans.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~趴在大理石阳台上，然后向普通美国人吐痰。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~turning this whole area to shit. Shit, people, shit.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~他把这里变成了魔窟。妈的，这些人，我操！

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Yep, when the hippies were distracted with weed and shit, those money guys never missed a beat.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~是的，虽然嬉皮士们正沉迷大麻之流，但有钱人的脚步从未停下。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~physical or psychological, that you sustain during the trip.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~不论是物理上的受伤还是精神上的创伤。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Welcome to your Higgins Tour, my name is Vicki,
~z~One thing that thrives is extreme sports;
~z~Well, that's it folks, you've seen the decline of the Roman Empire from the skies, choose Higgins again!
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~好了，观光结束了，你已经鸟瞰了罗马帝国的衰败。欢迎下次光临。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~I'll be your guide as we survey the crown jewel of capitalism, Liberty City.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~我会带你游览资本主义皇冠上的明珠，自由城。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~let's hope Ochoa has the stones to protect us all. Great view, huh?
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~希望控枪市长能靠石头保护我们。风景不错吧？

HT1AUD.original: ~z~home to artists and such, need I say more?
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~艺术家的栖身之处，还用说下去吗？

HT1AUD.original: ~z~He saved our tourism industry that day.
~z~Middle Park East, how the other half jog folks.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~中心公园东，上流阶层的锻炼之处。
~z~这个是哥伦布大教堂，漂亮吧？

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Man, those guards might be tubby, but they can move.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~伙计，楼下的保安确实挺胖，但他们很能跑。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~really shows how Liberty City brings people together,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~自由城居民凝聚力的最佳体现，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Leading us on to Broker, a borough that's particularly pleased with itself,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~再往前是Broker，一个十分安于现状的行政区，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~It was here that Ochoa eased safety restrictions on Helicopters and their pilots.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~Ochoa就是在这里放宽了对直升机及其飞行员的安全限制。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~The tall, clean buildings smooth enough to do lines of cocaine off of,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~耸立洁净的大楼，外墙平滑到可以在上面吸可卡因，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Union Drive, built during an unprecedented reign of organized crime,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~Union快速路，建成于有组织犯罪猖獗的时期，

HT1AUD.original: ~z~There's a guy lives in a bush, can get you anything that smokes. Anything.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~这里有个住草丛里的人，要什么都能给你弄来。什么都能。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Middle Park, a peaceful haven for so many LC residents,
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~中心公园，众多自由城居民的平静天堂。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~disappointing arty liberal kids with their ideas about how there's no God.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~其无神论的观念让附庸风雅的自由主义青少年失落沮丧。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~and ruining lives all over the country. Now that's how to get rich!
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~破坏各地人民的生活。这就是致富之道！

HT1AUD.original: ~z~History, it's right there, and we haven't learned a thing.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~历史的教训还在，而我们没有吸取任何教训。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Of course, once you've seen war, God is a joke, but would you look at that architecture?
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~当然，见过战争以后，上帝就是个笑话了，不过建筑还是值得欣赏的。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Now Firefly Island, where some remnants of the glory days can still be seen.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~这里是萤火虫乐园，在这儿还能找到往昔岁月的痕迹。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~and they would if they could people, mark my words.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~真有机会的话他们绝对会去试的，相信我。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Approaching Leaper's Bridge, still the record-holder for suicides.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~下面是纵身大桥，至今仍是自杀纪录保持者。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~and then the LCPD has to keep them apart.
~z~just a little reminder that we all need a guide through the rocky waters, don't we folks?
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~提醒我们需要指引才能通过岩礁带，不是吗？

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Higgins Tours wishes you a pleasant holiday.
~z~and only eighty-six murders last year, that's a record!
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~去年仅发生了86起谋杀案，再创新低！

HT1AUD.original: ~z~The Broker Bridge; an open invitation to terrorism,
~z~look closely, you might just get a peek!
~z~Well, here we are, I hope you've seen another side to Liberty City.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~好了，我们到了，希望你已经看到了自由城的另一面。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~sometimes it's the only option. Carpet bomb those leeches...
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~有时只能这么做，地毯式轰炸那些寄生虫...

HT1AUD.original: ~z~Remember to recommend Higgins Helitours to your friends.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~记得向你的朋友推荐Higgins直升机观光。

HT1AUD.original: ~z~where Mayor Ochoa makes all his important decisions to keep LC running smooth.
HT1AUD.translated: ~z~Ochoa市长于此作出各项重大决策，让自由城平稳运转。
